Name: Number of times 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' is performed per year.

Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': 'case:Amount > [amount_before_rejection]'}

Name: Frequency of 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' in relation to total number of rejections.
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by [ANY REJECTOR]'"}
